#sudo user 
proxy of root user

>create user
>set pass to it
>before granting sudo privilleges user should be created

//visudo /etc/sudoers.
#to create sudo user you have to make entry of user here
below root user you have to make entry for sudo user
ex test ALL=(ALL) ALL
:wq

